<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<p>
The <b>zig-zag</b> identities are a pair of identities satisfied
by the evaluation and coevaluation maps.
</p>
<p>
First zig-zag identity:
\[(\id_V\otimes\ev)(\coev\otimes\id_V) = \id_V.\]
<details>
<summary>
[explanation]
</summary>
\[
\begin{align*}
(\id_V\otimes\ev)(\coev\otimes\id_V)v
&= (\id_V\otimes\ev)(\coev\otimes\id_V)(1\otimes v)
= (\id_V\otimes\ev)(\coev\,1\otimes \id_Vv)\\[0.5em]
&= (\id_V\otimes\ev)
\left(\left(\sum_{i=1}^ne_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\otimes v\right)
= (\id_V\otimes\ev)
\left(\sum_{i=1}^n\left(e_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\otimes v\right)\\[0.5em]
&= \sum_{i=1}^n(\id_V\otimes\ev)
\left(\left(e_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\otimes v\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n(\id_V\otimes\ev)
\left(e_i\otimes(\pi^i\otimes v)\right)\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^n
\left(\id_Ve_i\otimes\ev(\pi^i\otimes v)\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n
\left(e_i\otimes\pi^iv\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n
\left(e_i\otimes v^i\right)\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^n
\left(v^ie_i\otimes 1\right)
= 
\left(\sum_{i=1}^nv^ie_i\right)\otimes 1
= v\otimes 1 = v.
\end{align*}
\]
</details>
</p>
<p>
Second zig-zag identity:
\[(\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})(\id_{V^*}\otimes\coev) = \id_{V^*}.\]
<details>
<summary>
[explanation]
</summary>
\[
\begin{align*}
(\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})(\id_{V^*}\otimes\coev)\alpha
&= (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})(\id_{V^*}\otimes\coev)(\alpha\otimes 1)
= (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})(\id_{V^*}\alpha\otimes\coev\,1)\\[0.5em]
&= (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})\left(\alpha\otimes\left(\sum_{i=1}^n e_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\right)
= (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})\left(\sum_{i=1}^n \alpha\otimes\left(e_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\right)\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^n (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})\left(\alpha\otimes\left(e_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n (\ev\otimes\id_{V^*})\left((\alpha\otimes e_i)\otimes\pi^i\right)\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^n \left(\ev(\alpha\otimes e_i)\otimes\id_{V^*}\pi^i\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n \left(\alpha(e_i)\otimes\pi^i\right)
= \sum_{i=1}^n \left(\alpha_i\otimes\pi^i\right)\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^n \left(1\otimes\alpha_i\pi^i\right)
= 1\otimes\left(\sum_{i=1}^n \alpha_i\pi^i\right)
= 1\otimes\alpha = \alpha.
\end{align*}
\]
</details>
</p>
</body>
</html>
